cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is about deep neural networks for visual recognition, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also proposes a new method for reducing computational complexity, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of smaller convolutional layers and feature co-occurrence is also related to neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the evaluation of the proposed method on various datasets involves multimedia (cs.MM) aspects.
